Creature tokens you control have flying.
Whenever Cloudbreacher Oktujo attacks, create a number of attacking 3/1 green Beast creature tokens equal to one plus the number of spells you’ve cast this turn. Exile those tokens at end of combat.

When Hunter’s Carapace enters, you may return target creature card with mana value 4 or less from your graveyard to the battlefield, then attach Hunter’s Carapace to it.
Equipped creature gets +1/+0 and has menace.
